articleTitle: Spekulationen über Barca-Interesse an Rapid-Talent Demir
articleTitleTranslated: Speculation about Barca interest in rapid talent Demir
articleContent: "Bin wegen eines anderen Spielers in Barcelona", dementierte sein Berater Öztürk die spanischen Medienberichte.
articleContentTranslated: "I'm in Barcelona because of another player", his agent Öztürk denied the Spanish media reports.
